<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>User Management - OneLastAI Admin</title>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
      color: #ffffff;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .admin-header {
      background: rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ff4444;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .admin-warning {
      color: #ff4444;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .hero-section {
      padding: 4rem 2rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.15) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 70%);
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ff4444;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff4444;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff4444, #cc0000, #ff6666);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    .hero-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff4444;
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: #e0e0e0;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .admin-content {
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .admin-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .admin-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.3);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 3rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .admin-card h3 {
      color: #ff4444;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .admin-card p {
      color: #b8b8b8;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .back-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff4444, #cc0000);
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .back-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(255, 68, 68, 0.4);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="admin-header">
    <div class="admin-warning">‚ö†Ô∏è RESTRICTED AREA - ADMIN ACCESS ONLY ‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-icon">üë•</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">User Management</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Manage user accounts and permissions</p>
  </section>

  <section class="admin-content">
    <div class="admin-grid">
      <div class="admin-card">
        <h3>üöß Under Development</h3>
        <p>
          This admin feature is currently being developed. Full administrative 
          capabilities will be available in the next release.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="admin-card">
        <h3>üîí Security Notice</h3>
        <p>
          All admin actions are logged and monitored. Ensure you have proper 
          authorization before accessing sensitive data.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="admin-card">
        <h3>üìä Quick Stats</h3>
        <p>
          System status: Online<br>
          Active users: 10,247<br>
          Agent requests: 1.2M today
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="/dashboard" class="back-button">‚Üê Back to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
